## **9. Installation Script** (setup.sh)

```bash name=setup.sh
#!/bin/bash

echo "🚀 Voting System MVP - Setup Script"
echo "===================================="

# Create root .env
echo "Creating .env files..."
cat > .env << EOF
NODE_ENV=development
MONGODB_URI=mongodb://localhost:27017/voting_system
JWT_SECRET=dev_secret_change_in_production
PAYSTACK_SECRET=sk_test_your_secret
PAYSTACK_PUBLIC=pk_test_your_public
ADMIN_EMAIL=admin@votingsystem.com
ADMIN_PASSWORD=Admin123!
EOF

# Setup backend
echo "Setting up backend..."
cd backend
cp .env.example .env.dev
npm install
cd ..

# Setup frontend
echo "Setting up frontend..."
cd frontend
cp .env.local.example .env.local
npm install
cd ..

echo ""
echo "✅ Setup complete!"
echo ""
echo "📝 Next steps:"
echo "1. Update .env files with your credentials"
echo "2. Start backend: cd backend && npm run dev"
echo "3. Start frontend: cd frontend && npm run dev"
echo "4. Open http://localhost:3000"
echo ""
